eceived her bachelors degree from central michigan university and a masters of business administration from the university of detroit  among her professional and community affiliations love served as a board member of the professional businesswomen of california and a member of association for corporate growth  she is a graduate from the center for creative leadership program was recognized as one of the bay area’s most influential women in business and serves on the california bankers association board of directors december  rss press contacts yolanda walkeryywalkercomericacom more › sustainabilitysustainability progress report tag cloudarizona california contest diversity dye earnings financial literacy florida greenwich excellence awards hatch houston identity theft index michigan middle market recycling ritchie shred day sustainability texas latest news jul  comerica declares dividend increase of  percent corporate informationcomerica bank tower  main street dallas texas   product information  directory information to find a comerica location near you visit wwwcomericacomlocal site navigation home personal business wealth management about comerica contact us newsroom careers investor relations fraud center diversity security privacy terms and conditions consumer complaint notice site map comerica bank member fdic equal opportunity lender equal housing lender e nmls id  español the brickmakers bride refined by love series  judith miller   christianbookcom hear about sales receive special offers  moreyou can unsubscribe at any time enter email address my account wishlist help email signup cart  items checkout welcome to christianbookcom sign in or create an account search by title author isbn etc dollar days shop  or less july music features search within all products books ebook music mp downloads accompaniment bibles homeschool gift  home dvds christian living children fiction software search bibles vbs church bible study books ebooks fiction homeschool music ki